invalid type: string "01:19:19.483 --> 01:19:24.163\n<v Kristian Purdy>Yeah, I'll tell you what. Let me just check your number now while I've got you. It's your number ending 746.</v>\n\n01:19:21.043 --> 01:19:21.523\n<v Sharon>Mhm.</v>\n\n01:19:23.883 --> 01:19:25.443\n<v Sharon>Aye, that's it.</v>\n\n01:19:25.843 --> 01:19:29.283\n<v Kristian Purdy>Alright, OK, I'm just sending go.</v>"˙˙˙˙˙˙˙˙˙